The dream has 2 main characters, a white dragon and a red dragon.\nThe white dragon is a computer genious and the red dragon is a destructive character that destroys all computers.\nThe computer genious goes to some kind of computer manufacturing plant and meets with another computer genious.\nThey build the most amazing computer system ever.\nThe computer system has no password.\nThe white dragon gets close to it and then the red dragon gets close to it and then the red dragon gets inside it.\nThe red dragon enjoys the computer system and gets stuck in it.\nThe white dragon destroys all the computers in some massive destruction.

